	<div class="title">
		<h1>Asian Appetite for Shark Fin Soup Destroying an Apex Predator</h1>                                    <div class="post-meta">
                        <span class="tags">
                            <a href="http://www.travelculturemag.com/tag/worldwide/">Worldwide</a>                         </span>
                        by <a href="#" class="author"><a href="http://www.travelculturemag.com/author/davidmcguire/" title="Posts by David McGuire" rel="author">David McGuire</a></a>
																					<span class="separator">|</span>
								on January 28, 2013													                                                    <span class="separator">|</span>
                            <a href="http://www.travelculturemag.com/asian-appetite-for-shark-fin-soup-destroying-an-apex-predator/#comments" class="anchor"><span class="dsq-postid" rel="2897 http://www.travelculturemag.com/?p=2897">3 comments</span></a>
                                                                            <span class="separator">|</span> in <a href="http://www.travelculturemag.com/category/ecotourism-sustainability/">
            Ecotourism &amp; Sustainability        </a>
                                <span class="separator">|</span>
                            <input type="hidden" class="love_it_hidden" id="hidden_2897" value="1">                            <a href="#" class="love_it" id="love_2897" ><span class="link-comments" style="">Like it</span></a>
